XMPP: It is great for messaging systems. Whatsapp uses the Ejabberd (XMPP) server for smooth and reliable message delivery.

WebSockets vs XMPP which is better choice for messaging/chat applications: 
  https://medium.com/@thinkwik/web-sockets-vs-xmpp-which-is-better-for-chat-application-113e3520b327


Gossip Protocol: It is used for spreading information across members of a network. It works by each member spreading information
to it's neighbours. thus spreading information to eventually all members. This is useful in use with consistent hashing. For example,
if one of the server goes down then information that this server is down can be spread to other servers on the ring using this strategy
